title: Vikings-Redskins TNF Recap, Cousins or Cook for Minnesota MVP? (Football 10/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to discuss the Vikings 19-9 victory over the Redskins on Thursday Night Football. The guys analyze when the game was lost for Washington, Kirk Cousins' MVP case and how to handle Dwayne Haskins, before hitting on news of the Pats trading Michael Bennett to the Cowboys and the Jets shopping some of their standouts.
